node.text:
@mrbeansg has launched the Mr Bean's E-shop and Home Delivery service. Now we can enjoy these delectable treats and drinks such as the Soya Milk Pouch, Soy Granola Bars and Almond Soya Milk while staying at home!
.
It's available to order via online at http://www.mrbean.com.sg/products and selected stores*, for take-aways and on GrabFood and Foodpanda.
.
#mrbeansg #burpple #burpplesg #stayhome #supportlocalfnb #savefnbsg #circuitbreakersg #circuitbreakerextended
